Student, admin, instructor login and grades assessment. 
MySQL database.
Home page.
Login Page.
Admin can change, update any data and also solve student-instructor technical problems.
Students can view grades, submit activities, ask queries and submit doubts.
Instructors can upload activities, upload grades, assess activity submissions, reply to student queries.

Grades represented using graphs developed using Canvas and Chart JS. Bar graphs used but others like pie charts are also available.
